    "message": "[Architect → Developer]\nArchitecture Design:\n\n```\n┌─────────────┐     ┌──────────────┐     ┌───────────┐\n│ FileWatcher │────▶│  EventBus    │────▶│ Dashboard │\n└─────────────┘     └──────────────┘     └───────────┘\n                           │\n                    ┌──────▼──────┐\n                    │ EventStore  │\n                    │ (SQLite)    │\n                    └─────────────┘\n```\n\nInterfaces:\n- IEventBus { on(event, handler), emit(event, data), off(event, handler) }\n- IFileWatcher { watch(path, options), unwatch(path) }\n- IEventStore { save(event), query(filters), getStats() }\n- IDashboard { render(), filter(type), clear() }\n\nTech Stack: TypeScript, Node.js fs.watch, SQLite via better-sqlite3\nPlease implement EventBus first, then FileWatcher, then Dashboard last.",
